sequenceDiagram
actor User
participant Browser
participant View as SongView
participant Formatter as SongFormatter
participant Strategy as FormattingStrategy
participant Cantandi as CantandiFormatting
participant Song as Piosenka

User->>Browser: Enable Cantandi mode
Browser->>View: toggle mode

View->>Formatter: format(song, mode="cantandiego")

Formatter->>Strategy: select CantandiFormatting
Strategy-->>Formatter: strategy selected

Formatter->>Cantandi: format(song)

Cantandi->>Song: read lyrics + chords
Song-->>Cantandi: text data

Cantandi->>Cantandi: apply chord highlighting

Cantandi-->>Formatter: formatted output
Formatter-->>View: formatted song

View-->>Browser: updated view
Browser-->>User: chords highlighted